      "description": "展示地图排名、评价、引用和本地关键词增长的专业本地SEO策略工作区。",
      "caption": "本地SEO策略覆盖 Google 商家档案、地图三强、引用建设和评价增长。",
      "inLanguage": "zh-Hans",
      "width": 1500,
      "height": 1000
    },
    {
      "@type": "ImageObject",
      "@id": "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/zh/local-seo-for-auckland-small-businesses/#consultationimage",
      "url": consultationImageUrl,
      "contentUrl": consultationImageUrl,
      "name": "奥克兰华人小企业本地搜索咨询",
